Idris DB includes additional enhancements and exclusive features developed by
IDRISIUM Corp / Idris Ghamid, including but not limited to:
- Better error messages with actionable solutions
- Smart logging system with multiple log levels
- Query performance analyzer with optimization suggestions
- Built-in data validation with custom validators
- Backup and restore functionality
- Smart caching layer for improved performance
- Real-time database statistics and monitoring
- Export/Import tools (JSON/CSV)
- Arabic language support and documentation
- Visual database inspector for debugging

All previous enhancements from Isar Plus are preserved:
- Enhanced web support with SQLite/WASM
- Additional query capabilities
- Performance improvements
- Bug fixes and stability enhancements

